    dc:description "FIGURES 78 – 85. Elytra of Indomias. Dorsal and Lateral views, 78 – 79, acutipennis (Boheman); 80 – 81, lividus (Marshall); lateral views, 82, perroteti (Boheman); 83, hispidus (Marshall); dorsal and lateral views, 84 – 85, praeteritus (Marshall)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193588>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 18. Head, dorsal view, of: Indomias. 10, anamalainus (Marshall); 11, ajaykumari sp. nov.; 12, prasinus (Boheman); 13, albizziae sp. nov.; 14, mangalai sp. nov.; 15, menoni sp. nov.; 16, praeteritus (Marshall); 17, marshalli sp. nov.; 18, yercaudensis sp. nov." ;
